# Per-extension CLAUDE.md and AGENTS.md files generated by `swamp repo init`
# The root CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md is the single source of project guidance
**/CLAUDE.md
**/AGENTS.md
!/CLAUDE.md
!/AGENTS.md

# Per-extension .claude/ directories managed by `swamp repo init/upgrade`
# Skills are bundled from the swamp binary, not authored in this repo.
# Intentionally blanket-ignores the whole directory — per-extension .gitignore
# entries for .claude/ sub-paths are swamp-managed but redundant here.
**/.claude/

# Git worktrees for isolated development
.worktrees/

# Swamp runtime state (databases, telemetry, caches, outputs)
# .swamp.yaml repo markers are NOT ignored — only the .swamp/ directory
**/.swamp/

# Session scratch files
next-prompt.md
